      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BERNARDO'S QUEEN (7) recorded her best time this course and distance last start, taking a Grade 5 in 29.83 by 4 lengths. Has the ability and expected to go close again. ASTON BUGSY (6) is racing well without winning, recording three minors on end, the latest hitting the ground running with a fast early sectional but finishing in the minors again when third (29.61) over 515m at Sandown. The form out of his last race has been franked. Hard to beat again. PAW FABIAN (1) ran below best last time finishing seventh (30.68) over 525m at this track from Box 6. Boasts a strong record from this draw with five wins and three minor placings from 12 starts. Can measure up this time. DO SOMETHING (2) picked up an unexpected cheque last time and is in the mix again.",
